<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AstraPitch AI - Revolutionary Pitch Intelligence</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary: #00d4ff;
            --secondary: #7c3aed;
            --accent: #f97316;
            --dark: #0a0e1a;
            --dark-2: #141824;
            --dark-3: #1e2337;
            --text: #e2e8f0;
            --text-dim: #94a3b8;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            background: var(--dark);
            color: var(--text);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .bg-stars {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom, #1e2337 0%, #0a0e1a 100%);
        }

        .star {
            position: absolute;
            width: 2px;
            height: 2px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: twinkle 3s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes twinkle {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; }
            50% { opacity: 1; }
        }

        .glow-orb {
            position: absolute;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(100px);
            opacity: 0.2;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .orb-1 {
            background: var(--primary);
            top: -200px;
            right: -100px;
            animation: float 15s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        .orb-2 {
            background: var(--secondary);
            bottom: -200px;
            left: -100px;
            animation: float 20s infinite ease-in-out reverse;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
            50% { transform: translate(50px, 50px) scale(1.1); }
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
            background: rgba(10, 14, 26, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
            animation: slideDown 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from {
                transform: translateY(-100%);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--primary);
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 6rem 2rem 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 900px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(40px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            line-height: 1.2;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.2s backwards;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.4s backwards;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            justify-content: center;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.6s backwards;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--dark);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* Features Section */
        .features {
            padding: 8rem 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), white);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .features-grid {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 35, 55, 0.6), rgba(20, 24, 36, 0.6));
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: all 0.4s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .feature-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1), transparent);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s;
        }

        .feature-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* Analyzer Section */
        .analyzer {
            padding: 8rem 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.03));
        }

        .analyzer-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .upload-area {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 35, 55, 0.8), rgba(20, 24, 36, 0.8));
            border: 2px dashed var(--primary);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .upload-area::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -2px;
            left: -2px;
            right: -2px;
            bottom: -2px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary), var(--accent));
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            z-index: -1;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .upload-area:hover::before {
            opacity: 0.2;
        }

        .upload-area:hover {
            border-color: var(--secondary);
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .upload-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 200px;
            background: rgba(30, 35, 55, 0.8);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            resize: vertical;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .plan-selector {
            margin: 2rem 0;
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .plan-option {
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border: 2px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: rgba(30, 35, 55, 0.6);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .plan-option.active {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2), rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.2));
        }

        .analysis-result {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 35, 55, 0.8), rgba(20, 24, 36, 0.8));
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 2rem;
            display: none;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        .analysis-result.show {
            display: block;
        }

        .loading {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .spinner {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border: 4px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
            border-top-color: var(--primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        /* Pricing Section */
        .pricing {
            padding: 8rem 2rem;
        }

        .pricing-grid {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .pricing-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 35, 55, 0.8), rgba(20, 24, 36, 0.8));
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
            border: 2px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.4s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .pricing-card.featured {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .pricing-card.featured::before {
            content: 'POPULAR';
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: -35px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--secondary));
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 3rem;
            transform: rotate(45deg);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .pricing-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.02);
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .plan-name {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .plan-price {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
        }

        .plan-price span {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        .plan-features {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .plan-features li {
            padding: 1rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .plan-features li::before {
            content: '✓';
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .plan-features li.con {
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .plan-features li.con::before {
            content: '✗';
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: rgba(10, 14, 26, 0.9);
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
        }

        footer p {
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }

            .features-grid,
            .pricing-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .pricing-card.featured {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        .file-input-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        #fileInput {
            display: none;
        }

        .file-label {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2), rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.2));
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .file-label:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .file-name {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .score-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .score-excellent {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669);
        }

        .score-good {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #0ea5e9);
        }

        .score-fair {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, var(--accent));
        }

        .score-poor {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #dc2626);
        }

        .recommendation-section {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .recommendation-section h3 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .recommendation-item {
            background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-stars" id="stars"></div>
    <div class="glow-orb orb-1"></div>
    <div class="glow-orb orb-2"></div>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="logo">ASTRAPITCH AI</div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
                <li><a href="#analyzer">Analyzer</a></li>
                <li><a href="#pricing">Pricing</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Revolutionary Pitch Intelligence</h1>
            <p>Harness the power of advanced AI to analyze, optimize, and perfect your investment and business pitches with unparalleled precision.</p>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a href="#analyzer" class="btn btn-primary">Analyze Your Pitch</a>
                <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-secondary">View Pricing</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features" id="features">
        <h2 class="section-title">Why AstraPitch AI?</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
                <h3>Precision Analysis</h3>
                <p>Our AI evaluates every aspect of your pitch—from market potential to financial projections—with institutional-grade accuracy.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
                <h3>Instant Feedback</h3>
                <p>Get comprehensive analysis in seconds, not days. Upload your pitch and receive actionable insights immediately.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
                <h3>Context-Aware Insights</h3>
                <p>Pro plan analyzes your pitch against specific companies and stocks, providing tailored recommendations based on real market data.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
                <h3>Secure & Confidential</h3>
                <p>Your pitches are encrypted and never shared. We maintain the highest standards of data security and privacy.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">📄</div>
                <h3>Multi-Format Support</h3>
                <p>Upload text or PDF documents. Our AI seamlessly processes both formats with equal precision.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🚀</div>
                <h3>Continuous Learning</h3>
                <p>Our AI is trained on thousands of successful pitches and continuously improves to stay ahead of market trends.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Analyzer Section -->
    <section class="analyzer" id="analyzer">
        <div class="analyzer-container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Analyze Your Pitch</h2>
            
            <div class="plan-selector">
                <div class="plan-option active" data-plan="basic">
                    <h4>Basic (Free)</h4>
                    <p>General Recommendations</p>
                </div>
                <div class="plan-option" data-plan="pro">
                    <h4>Pro</h4>
                    <p>AI-Powered + Context Analysis</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="upload-area" id="uploadArea">
                <div class="upload-icon">📤</div>
                <h3>Upload Your Pitch or Paste Text</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 1rem;">Supports PDF and text formats</p>
                <div class="file-input-wrapper">
                    <input type="file" id="fileInput" accept=".pdf,.txt">
                    <label for="fileInput" class="file-label">Choose PDF File</label>
                    <div class="file-name" id="fileName"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <textarea id="pitchText" placeholder="Or paste your pitch text here..."></textarea>

            <div id="companyInput" style="display: none; margin-top: 2rem;">
                <input type="text" id="companyName" placeholder="Enter company/stock symbol (e.g., AAPL, Tesla)" 
                    style="width: 100%; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(30, 35, 55, 0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); border-radius: 12px; color: var(--text); font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;">
            </div>

            <button class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 2rem;" onclick="analyzePitch()">
                Analyze Pitch
            </button>

            <div class="analysis-result" id="analysisResult">
                <div class="loading" id="loading">
                    <div class="spinner"></div>
                    <p>Analyzing your pitch with advanced AI...</p>
                </div>
                <div id="resultContent" style="display: none;"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Section -->
    <section class="pricing" id="pricing">
        <h2 class="section-title">Choose Your Plan</h2>
        <div class="pricing-grid">
            <div class="pricing-card">
                <h3 class="plan-name">Basic</h3>
                <div class="plan-price">FREE</div>
                <ul class="plan-features">
                    <li>Text & PDF upload support</li>
                    <li>Core pitch analysis</li>
                    <li>General recommendations</li>
                    <li>Structure & clarity feedback</li>
                    <li>Basic scoring system</li>
                    <li class="con">No AI-powered insights</li>
                    <li class="con">No company-specific analysis</li>
                    <li class="con">No market context</li>
                </ul>
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" style="width: 100%;">Get Started Free</button>
            </div>

            <div class="pricing-card featured">
                <h3 class="plan-name">Pro</h3>
                <div class="plan-price">COMING SOON</div>
                <ul class="plan-features">
                    <li>Everything in Basic</li>
                    <li>Advanced AI-powered analysis</li>
                    <li>Company-specific insights</li>
                    <li>Stock market context</li>
                    <li>Competitive comparison</li>
                    <li>Industry benchmarking</li>
                    <li>Real-time market data integration</li>
                    <li>Detailed improvement roadmap</li>
                    <li>Priority support</li>
                </ul>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; opacity: 0.7; cursor: not-allowed;">Coming Soon</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 AstraPitch AI. Revolutionizing pitch analysis with artificial intelligence.</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Generate stars
        const starsContainer = document.getElementById('stars');
        for (let i = 0; i < 100; i++) {
            const star = document.createElement('div');
            star.className = 'star';
            star.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
            star.style.top = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
            star.style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 3 + 's';
            starsContainer.appendChild(star);
        }

        // Plan selector
        document.querySelectorAll('.plan-option').forEach(option => {
            option.addEventListener('click', function() {
                document.querySelectorAll('.plan-option').forEach(o => o.classList.remove('active'));
                this.classList.add('active');
                const plan = this.dataset.plan;
                const companyInput = document.getElementById('companyInput');
                if (plan === 'pro') {
                    companyInput.style.display = 'block';
                } else {
                    companyInput.style.display = 'none';
                }
            });
        });

        // File input
        document.getElementById('fileInput').addEventListener('change', function(e) {
            const fileName = document.getElementById('fileName');
            if (e.target.files.length > 0) {
                fileName.textContent = '📄 ' + e.target.files[0].name;
            } else {
                fileName.textContent = '';
            }
        });

        // Smooth scrolling
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                const target = document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href'));
                if (target) {
                    target.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
                }
            });
        });

        // Analysis function (Basic plan - rule-based)
        function analyzeBasicPitch(text) {
            const words = text.trim().split(/\s+/).length;
            const hasProblem = text.toLowerCase().includes('problem') || text.toLowerCase().includes('issue');
            const hasSolution = text.toLowerCase().includes('solution') || text.toLowerCase().includes('solve');
            const hasMarket = text.toLowerCase().includes('market') || text.toLowerCase().includes('customer');
            const hasFinancials = text.toLowerCase().includes('revenue') || text.toLowerCase().includes('profit') || text.toLowerCase().includes('$');
            
            let score = 0;
            let recommendations = [];
            
            // Scoring
            if (words >= 100) score += 20;
            else recommendations.push('Expand your pitch to at least 100 words for better coverage');
            
            if (hasProblem) score += 20;
            else recommendations.push('Clearly define the problem you\'re solving');
            
            if (hasSolution) score += 20;
            else recommendations.push('Articulate your solution more explicitly');
            
            if (hasMarket) score += 20;
            else recommendations.push('Include market size and target customer information');
            
            if (hasFinancials) score += 20;
            else recommendations.push('Add financial projections or revenue model');
            
            // Additional checks
            if (words < 50) recommendations.push('Pitch is too brief - add more detail about your business');
            if (text.split('.').length < 5) recommendations.push('Use more complete sentences to improve clarity');
            if (!text.includes('unique') && !text.includes('different')) recommendations.push('Highlight what makes you unique or different from competitors');
            
            let scoreClass = 'score-poor';
            let scoreLabel = 'Needs Improvement';
            if (score >= 80) { scoreClass = 'score-excellent'; scoreLabel = 'Excellent'; }
            else if (score >= 60) { scoreClass = 'score-good'; scoreLabel = 'Good'; }
            else if (score >= 40) { scoreClass = 'score-fair'; scoreLabel = 'Fair'; }
            
            return { score, scoreClass, scoreLabel, recommendations };
        }

        // Main analyze function
        async function analyzePitch() {
            const pitchText = document.getElementById('pitchText').value.trim();
            const fileInput = document.getElementById('fileInput');
            const selectedPlan = document.querySelector('.plan-option.active').dataset.plan;
            const companyName = document.getElementById('companyName').value.trim();
            
            if (!pitchText && fileInput.files.length === 0) {
                alert('Please enter pitch text or upload a file');
                return;
            }

            // Show results section
            const analysisResult = document.getElementById('analysisResult');
            const loading = document.getElementById('loading');
            const resultContent = document.getElementById('resultContent');
            
            analysisResult.classList.add('show');
            loading.style.display = 'block';
            resultContent.style.display = 'none';

            // Simulate processing time
            await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 2000));

            let result;
            
            if (selectedPlan === 'basic') {
                // Basic plan - rule-based analysis
                let textToAnalyze = pitchText;
                if (fileInput.files.length > 0) {
                    // In a real implementation, you'd extract text from PDF here
                    textToAnalyze = pitchText || 'PDF content would be extracted here...';
                }
                
                result = analyzeBasicPitch(textToAnalyze);
                
                resultContent.innerHTML = `
                    <h3 style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Analysis Complete</h3>
                    <div class="score-badge ${result.scoreClass}">Score: ${result.score}/100 - ${result.scoreLabel}</div>
                    
                    <div class="recommendation-section">
                        <h3>Recommendations</h3>
                        ${result.recommendations.map(rec => `<div class="recommendation-item">${rec}</div>`).join('')}
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1); border-radius: 12px; border-left: 3px solid var(--secondary);">
                        <h4 style="color: var(--secondary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">💎 Upgrade to Pro</h4>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-dim);">Get AI-powered insights, company-specific analysis, and market context to take your pitch to the next level.</p>
                    </div>
                `;
            } else {
                // Pro plan - would use API here
                if (!companyName) {
                    alert('Please enter a company or stock symbol for Pro analysis');
                    loading.style.display = 'none';
                    return;
                }
                
                resultContent.innerHTML = `
                    <h3 style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Pro Analysis Complete</h3>
                    <div class="score-badge score-excellent">Score: 87/100 - Excellent</div>
                    
                    <div class="recommendation-section">
                        <h3>AI-Powered Insights for ${companyName}</h3>
                        <div class="recommendation-item">
                            <strong>Market Context:</strong> Your pitch aligns well with current ${companyName} market trends. The sector is experiencing 23% YoY growth.
                        </div>
                        <div class="recommendation-item">
                            <strong>Competitive Position:</strong> Similar to ${companyName}'s early positioning, but consider emphasizing differentiation more clearly.
                        </div>
                        <div class="recommendation-item">
                            <strong>Financial Projections:</strong> Your revenue model is realistic compared to ${companyName}'s trajectory. Consider adding unit economics.
                        </div>
                        <div class="recommendation-item">
                            <strong>Risk Assessment:</strong> Market risks are well-addressed. Add more detail on operational scaling challenges.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1); border-radius: 12px;">
                        <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Next Steps</h4>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-dim);">Based on ${companyName}'s investor preferences, focus on: scalability metrics, customer acquisition costs, and long-term competitive moats.</p>
                    </div>
                `;
            }

            loading.style.display = 'none';
            resultContent.style.display = 'block';
        }
    </script>
